<div class="container" style='padding: 0;'>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-lg-6">
      <div id="result" >
        <a href='<%= $SUB_DIRECTORY %>/img/sample.png' data-lightbox="sample">
          <img style="max-width:100%; max-height:100%; " alt="RSyntaxTree Sample" src="<%= $SUB_DIRECTORY %>/img/sample.png" />
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class='text-right' style="margin-bottom:10px; line-height: 100%;">
        <sub>
          左クリックでズーム，右クリックで画像保存<br />
          画像エリアとテキストエリアは縦方向にサイズ変更可能
        </sub>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="col-lg-6">
      <div id="status" style="min-height:1.5em; padding-left: 1em; margin-top: 5px; background-color: #484848	;">
        <span id="alert">
          <span class='text text-info'>●</span> <span class='alertmessage'></span>
        </span>
      </div>
      <div class='anchor' id='rst-editor'></div>

      <div id='editor'><%= $SAMPLE1 %></div>

      <div class='text-right' style="margin-bottom:10px; line-height: 100%;">
        <sub>
          バージョン1.0では，樹形図描画の構文が大幅に刷新されました．詳しくは<br /> <a href="https://yohasebe.github.io/rsyntaxtree/documentation_ja">使い方</a> および <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://yohasebe.github.io/rsyntaxtree/examples">ギャラリー</a> を参照してください．
        </sub>
      </div>

      <div  class='text-right'>
        <div class="row" style="margin-top:15px; margin-bottom:15px;">
          <div class="col-sm-12">
            <div style="display:inline">
              <input type="checkbox" value="" id="auto-bracket">
              <label for="auto-bracket">
                <small>括弧を自動で閉じる</small>
              </label>&nbsp;&nbsp;
            </div>
            <button type='button' class='btn btn-sm btn-light' id="check"><i class="far fa-check-square"></i><small> 括弧の対応チェック</small></button>&nbsp;
            <button type='button' class='btn btn-sm btn-light' id="clear"><i class="fas fa-eraser"></i><small> クリア</small></button>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row" style="margin-bottom:15px; margin-top:15px;">
          <div class="col-sm-4">
            <button class='btn btn-primary draw btn-block' id='draw_png' type='submit'><i class="fas fa-pencil-ruler"></i> Draw <b>PNG</b></button>
          </div>
          <div class="col-sm-4">
            <button class='btn btn-primary draw btn-block' id='draw_svg' type='submit'><i class="fas fa-pencil-ruler"></i> Draw <b>SVG</b></button>
          </div>
          <div class="col-sm-4">
            <button class='btn btn-secondary draw btn-block' id='download_pdf' type='submit'><i class="fas fa-file-pdf"></i> Download <b>PDF</b></button>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="container" style='margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom:20px; padding: 0;'>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-3">
      <label for="leafstyle">コネクタの形状</label>
      <select class="form-control" name='leafstyle' id='leafstyle'>
        <option value='auto'>自動</option>
        <option value='bar'>縦線のみ</option>
        <option value='nothing'>なし</option>
      </select>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-3">
      <label for="leafstyle">フォント・スタイル</label>
      <select class="form-control" name='fontstyle'>
        <option value='noto-serif'>Noto Serif</option>
        <option value='noto-sans'>Noto Sans</option>
        <option value='noto-sans-mono'>Noto Sans Mono</option>
        <option value='cjk'>WQY Zen Hei (CJK)</option>
      </select>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-3">
      <label for="leafstyle">フォント・サイズ</label>
      <select class="form-control" name='fontsize'>
        <option value='6'>6</option>
        <option value='8'>8</option>
        <option value='10'>10</option>
        <option value='12'>12</option>
        <option value='14'>14</option>
        <option selected='selected' value='16'>16</option>
        <option value='18'>18</option>
        <option value='20'>20</option>
        <option value='22'>22</option>
        <option value='24'>24</option>
        <option value='26'>26</option>
      </select>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-3">
      <label for="leafstyle">カラー</label>
      <select class="form-control" name='color'>
        <option value='modern'>Modern</option>
        <option value='traditional' selected='selected'>Traditional</option>
        <option value='none'>なし</option>
      </select>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-3">
      <label for="leafstyle">コネクタの高さ</label>
      <select class="form-control" name='vheight'>
        <option value='0.5'>0.5</option>
        <option value='1.0'>1.0</option>
        <option value='1.5'>1.5</option>
        <option value='2.0' selected='selected'>2.0</option>
        <option value='3.0'>3.0</option>
        <option value='4.0'>4.0</option>
        <option value='5.0'>5.0</option>
      </select>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-3">
      <label for="leafstyle">線の幅</label>
      <select class="form-control" name='linewidth'>
        <option value='1' selected='selected'>1</option>
        <option value='2'>2</option>
        <option value='3'>3</option>
        <option value='4'>4</option>
        <option value='5'>5</option>
      </select>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-3"></div>
    <div class="col-md-3"></div>
  </div>

  <div class='row'>
    <div class='col-md-3'>
      <label for="color">折れ線コネクタ</label><br />
      <div class="btn-group btn-group-toggle" data-toggle="buttons">
        <label class="btn btn-light active">
          <input type="radio" name="polyline" value="on" autocomplete="off"> On
        </label>
        <label class="btn btn-light">
          <input type="radio" name="polyline" value="off" autocomplete="off" checked> Off
        </label>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class='col-md-3'>
      <label for="transparent">背景の透過</label><br />
      <div class="btn-group btn-group-toggle" data-toggle="buttons">
        <label class="btn btn-light active">
          <input type="radio" name="transparent" value="on" autocomplete="off"> On
        </label>
        <label class="btn btn-light">
          <input type="radio" name="transparent" value="off" autocomplete="off" checked> Off
        </label>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class='col-md-3'>
      <label for="symmetrize">極端な左右対象化</label><br />
      <div class="btn-group btn-group-toggle" data-toggle="buttons">
        <label class="btn btn-light active">
          <input type="radio" name="symmetrize" value="on" autocomplete="off" > On
        </label>
        <label class="btn btn-light">
          <input type="radio" name="symmetrize" value="off" autocomplete="off" checked> Off
        </label>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class='col-md-3'>
      <label for="hide_default_connectors">デフォルトのコネクタを隠す</label><br />
      <div class="btn-group btn-group-toggle" data-toggle="buttons">
        <label class="btn btn-light active">
          <input type="radio" name="hide_default_connectors" value="on" autocomplete="off" > On
        </label>
        <label class="btn btn-light">
          <input type="radio" name="hide_default_connectors" value="off" autocomplete="off" checked> Off
        </label>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>
